headline: Blastr Green Steel announces new strategic investment to minimize water usage and discharge
summary: Blastr Green Steel (Blastr) has announced a new strategic investor in its latest round of financing, aiming to collaborate on best-in-class water systems at its flagship ultra-low CO2 steel plant in Finland.
